{"tid":1456433,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"決定離開深藍公司 想知有冇得拎Annual Bonus","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:51:22.000Z","uid":39137,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd0fc6e79d591e09bf1d77d4143b3f581bcacb2","tid":1456433,"uid":39137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"開錯左係吹水台 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經厭倦留係公司 有D商家佬眼入邊只係識得擁抱大灣區<br />\n但我想知拎唔拎到「Annual Bonus」<br />\n而其實呢份Annual Bonus即係等於13個月糧<br />\n合約上寫有幾個條件<br />\n1. 跟12月糧發放<br />\n2. 工作滿12個月就可以獲得相當於1個月既薪金<br />\n3. 工作未滿12個月可以按比例發放<br />\n4. 僱員於12月前離職將不獲發放<br />\n<br />\n第4點係咪即係指我而家辭職係冇機會按比例得到第13個月糧？<br />\n因為根據第8章「部分年終酬金」<br />\n第4點好似係同勞工法有抵觸<br />\n另一個角度睇⋯⋯<br />\n如果我係被解雇(並非因失職而即時解僱，有一個月通知期)<br />\n佢係咪一定要按比例出Annual Bonus比我？<br />\n<br />\n勞工法懶人link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/EO_guide_full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2FEO_guide_full.pdf&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=50e83bf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/EO_guide_full.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"5c5457e67cfbdf2ef3c58700343284ab63f5150e","tid":1456433,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"bonus 唔等如13mth pay<br />\n大可以唔俾你"},{"pid":"9a0caa87199036b8444fb215b06c4eb42b0ac3da","tid":1456433,"uid":131312,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"你自己走冇，佢炒你有部份拎"},{"pid":"a602b2885dbd54c67bc22c9f68f784c2d4f0a1f9","tid":1456433,"uid":57462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"寫明double pay 13th month pay 你贏<br />\n寫bonus / discretionary 你輸"},{"pid":"37e86ca5eb8986c5e74d0cb8dc013c10e1ca628a","tid":1456433,"uid":131312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"